dataFrame <- read.csv("/Users/spiderfencer/Downloads/oasis_cross-sectional.csv", header=TRUE, sep=",")
names(dataFrame)
##  [1] "ID"    "M.F"   "Hand"  "Age"   "Educ"  "SES"   "MMSE"  "CDR"   "eTIV" 
## [10] "nWBV"  "ASF"   "Delay"
neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(7,9)])
plot(neededData$eTIV, neededData$MMSE)
abline(lm(MMSE ~ eTIV, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(8,9)])
plot(neededData$eTIV, neededData$CDR)
abline(lm(CDR ~ eTIV, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(7,10)])
plot(neededData$nWBV, neededData$MMSE)
abline(lm(MMSE ~ nWBV, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(8,10)])
plot(neededData$nWBV, neededData$CDR)
abline(lm(CDR ~ nWBV, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(6,8)])
plot(neededData$SES, neededData$CDR)
abline(lm(CDR ~ SES, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(6,7)])
plot(neededData$SES, neededData$MMSE)
abline(lm(MMSE ~ SES, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(6,9)])
plot(neededData$SES, neededData$eTIV)
abline(lm(eTIV ~ SES, data=neededData))

neededData = na.omit(dataFrame[,c(6,10)])
plot(neededData$SES, neededData$nWBV)
abline(lm(nWBV ~ SES, data=neededData))
